{{template "layout" .}}

{{define "title"}}Privacy Policy - CASCI{{end}}

{{define "content"}}
<div class="container">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    
    <p class="last-updated">Last updated: December 17, 2025</p>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>Introduction</h2>
        <p>This privacy policy describes how CASCI (CI/CD Application Server for Continuous Integration) collects, uses, and protects your information.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
        <h3>Account Information</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Username and email address (for account creation)</li>
            <li>Hashed passwords (bcrypt, never stored in plain text)</li>
            <li>API tokens (encrypted)</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Usage Data</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Build logs and execution history</li>
            <li>Project configurations and settings</li>
            <li>Node status and metrics</li>
            <li>API request logs (IP address, timestamp, endpoint)</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Provide and maintain CI/CD services</li>
            <li>Authenticate and authorize access</li>
            <li>Execute builds and manage pipelines</li>
            <li>Send notifications about build status</li>
            <li>Monitor system health and performance</li>
            <li>Maintain security and prevent abuse</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>Data Storage and Security</h2>
        <h3>Storage</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>All data stored in database (SQLite, PostgreSQL, or MySQL)</li>
            <li>Credentials encrypted with AES-256-GCM</li>
            <li>Build logs stored on filesystem with access controls</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Security Measures</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>HTTPS/TLS encryption for all connections</li>
            <li>Password hashing with bcrypt</li>
            <li>JWT tokens for session management</li>
            <li>Role-based access control (RBAC)</li>
            <li>Audit logging of security events</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>Data Retention</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Build Logs</strong>: 90 days (configurable per project)</li>
            <li><strong>Audit Logs</strong>: 90 days, then automatically cleaned</li>
            <li><strong>User Accounts</strong>: Retained until explicitly deleted</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You have the right to:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Access your personal data</li>
            <li>Correct inaccurate data</li>
            <li>Delete your account and associated data</li>
            <li>Export your data</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have questions about this privacy policy:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="/server/contact">Contact Form</a></li>
            <li>Email: privacy@casapps.us</li>
            <li><a href="https://github.com/casapps/casci/issues" target="_blank">GitHub Issues</a></li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</div>
{{end}}
